<body>

    <section>
        <div class="container mt-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="jumbotron">
                    <h3 class="display-5">ASKING FOR ADMINISTRATORS PERMISSION</h3>
                    <br>
                    <p class="lead"><b><%= username %></b> Institution hereby declare that the information furnished above is true, complete and correct to the best of my knowledge and belief. understand that in the event of my information being found false or incorrect
